msgctxt "92_Homeless Man"
msgid "Hey, Akiyama, is that you?"
msgstr "Buenas, ¿Hablo con Akiyama?"

msgctxt "104_Akiyama"
msgid "Uh-huh. You find him?"
msgstr "Ajá. ¿Lo encontraste?"

msgctxt "116_Homeless Man"
msgid "Yup. My buddy said he was skulkin' around Pink Street."
msgstr "Sep. Mi amigo dice que anda por la Calle Pink."

msgctxt "128_Homeless Man"
msgid "Couldn't believe how much he looked like the picture, neither."
msgstr "No puedo creer lo mucho que se parece al dibujo."

msgctxt "140_Akiyama"
msgid "Wow, that's pretty incredible. Okay, I'll go check it out.\\r\n"
"Thanks. I owe you one."
msgstr "Wow, eso es increíble. Bueno, iré a verlo. Muchas gracias\\r\n"
"Te debo una."

msgctxt "152_Homeless Man"
msgid "Aw, it's nothin'! See ya later."
msgstr "Bah, ¡No es nada! Nos vemos."

msgctxt "212_Akiyama"
msgid "(Pink Street, huh...? If I hurry, I might still catch him.)"
msgstr "(Calle Pink, ¿Ah...? Si me apresuro, quizás lo atrape.)"

